name: Charging Station Management CMS Template
description:
Easy Charge CMS UI kit for Figma is a modern UI kit template for EV Companies. Easy Charge UI kit is built with fully customization CMS templates and UI components. You can update with your own branded content, fonts & colors to fit your application project.


Features:

  • 70+ CMS Screens
  • Pixel perfect screen designs
  • Smart Layout Features
  • Grouped and Organized
  • Free Font
  • Customization Components
  • Figma Format file
